'''Danielle''' is the girlfriend of [[Charlie Mitchell]].

==History==
Danielle was in bed with her boyfriend, Charlie, when the building collapsed. Danielle was uninjured in the collapsed, but Charlie had to be taken to the hospital. Danielle came to the hospital and was told of Charlie's injuries and that he'd need surgery. After his surgery, she was told he'd be okay and asked to see him.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is dating [[Charlie Mitchell]]. However, she is unaware that he is married.
